    <item>
      <title>加拿大总理特鲁多在海湖庄园与特朗普举行重要会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/canada-s-trudeau-arrives-in-florida-for-meeting-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多于周五会见了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普，这位即将上任的美国领导人威胁要对邻国实施新的关税，除非它们阻止非法毒品和无证移民跨境流动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/canada-s-trudeau-arrives-in-florida-for-meeting-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 22:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰大选结果接近，出口民调显示哈里斯总理和新芬党支持率持平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/irish-pm-harris-almost-level-with-sinn-fein-in-exit-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰总理西蒙·哈里斯领导的爱尔兰统一党在大选中与新芬党势均力敌，这表明他提前前往爱尔兰的决定并未带来他预期的优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/irish-pm-harris-almost-level-with-sinn-fein-in-exit-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 22:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的“独狼式”袭击对习近平的安全国家构成挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/china-s-lone-wolf-attacks-pose-challenge-for-xi-s-security-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平建立了庞大的安全体系，以防止暴力势力破坏社会稳定。新一轮致命袭击事件给官员们带来了扩大监控范围的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/china-s-lone-wolf-attacks-pose-challenge-for-xi-s-security-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 22:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果北约保护未占领地区，泽连斯基愿意停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/zelenskiy-suggests-cease-fire-if-nato-protects-unoccupied-land</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，他愿意接受与俄罗斯的停火协议，允许乌克兰部分地区被占领，以换取北约对其余地区的安全保障，这是迄今为止最强烈​​的信号，表明乌克兰领导人愿意在不收复所有领土的情况下结束战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/zelenskiy-suggests-cease-fire-if-nato-protects-unoccupied-land</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 21:13:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
